Title: Enemies Abound
Description:
<Hannan is barely responsive and less corporeal than he should be, lost deeper in the Unseeming than you.>

Some of the canisters exploded... Then the spiders appeared.

Kill the--kill the spiders!
ObjectivesCompletionText: Regroup with Hannan and Orweyna outside the Abandoned Harvest Site cave in the Salien Gutters.
RewardText: Hmm. I have noticed you seem good at surviving challenging tasks. I will remember this about you.
